&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span&gt;Clinical Psychologist / Neuropsychologist &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We’re looking for an experienced clinical psychologist / neuropsychologist to input into our innovative multiprofessional community brain injury rehab and stroke rehab services. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span&gt;Supported by an Assistant Psychologist, you would provide advice to patients, families and colleagues, assessment (including neuropsychological assessment), and direct therapeutic input on an individual, couple or group basis. Supervision and teaching also form part of the remit.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The post is part of a small, cohesive Health Psychology service which works closely with a variety of MDTs, with Trust senior management and local partner bodies (e.g. Mental Health Trust).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Herefordshire itself is a largely rural setting which offers opportunities and challenges of its own: you would at times be dealing with problems of geographical access, deprivation and diversity/discrimination issues which may be somewhat different to urban settings, but are no less significant. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;For many of us who work in Herefordshire, the easy access to nature and outdoor activity in this beautiful county, alongside affordable housing, offer significant quality of life benefits, while the amenities of Birmingham, Cardiff and Bristol are all easily reached.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you’d like to learn more, please contact Dr Emma Nicholas Clinical Psychologist on &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;emma.nicholas2@wvt.nhs.uk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;, or Dr Ray Owen, Consultant Clinical Psychologist on &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;ray.owen@wvt.nhs.uk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt; , or phone 01432 347697&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Interviews (probably by video) for shortlisted candidates are scheduled to take place in the week commencing 30&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;th&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt; November&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
